net.proteusframework.cms

Annotation Type PageElementModelConfiguration


  • @Documented
 @Retention(value=RUNTIME)
 @Target(value=TYPE)
 @Component
public @interface PageElementModelConfiguration
    PageElement related configuration information. Provides static/default configuration for a PageElementModelFactory. Do not call these methods directly. Use an PageElementModel instead.
    Author:
    Russ Tennant (russ@proteus.co)

    • Required Element Summary

      Required Elements 
      Modifier and Type Required Element and Description
      java.lang.String name
      The name of the PageElementModel.

    • Optional Element Summary

      Optional Elements 
      Modifier and Type Optional Element and Description
      boolean assignedByDefault
      True to assign this to new Sites by default.
      java.lang.Class<? extends DelegationHelper> delegationHelper
      Optional delegation helper for PageElements that support PageElement delegation.
      java.lang.Class<? extends Editor> editor
      The editor value.
      boolean enabled
      Return true if the PageElement is enabled.
      java.lang.String iconPath
      Icon path.
      boolean supportsLabels
      Return true if the PageElement should support labels.
